title: #100: Final Episodes of 13 Reasons Why
description:
The RCP team (Jim Clemente, Laura Richards and Lisa Zambetti) cover the last 4 episodes of the Netflix Show Thirteen Reasons Why. Jim and Laura provide insight and analysis and highlight the important learning points from this show.
